{"tid":446083,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"FG的抉擇","createTime":"2017-10-24T03:58:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-08T07:30:42.000Z","uid":60219,"like":1,"dislike":34,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"993905d839fa8a82f82f1bd0df09e0b185bcf7d7","tid":446083,"uid":60219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T03:58:34.000Z","msg":"我今年final year，呢排忙緊見工<br />\n<br />\n前排A公司出30k既offer比我<br />\n<br />\n其實我等緊B公司份50k既offer，B公司既工作性質同埋成就感都比A公司高，但最衰就係B公司係絕無例外11月尾先出offer<br />\n<br />\n如果我而家接咗A公司既offer，日後我又接B公司既offer，呢行行規係我會需要承受賠償既風險，亦有可能被人告<br />\n<br />\n我無父幹無樓無車，到底我應該點選擇?<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 保守d揀A公司，起碼保證到日後買到樓<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 趁後生搏一舖啦屌你，搏盡無悔啊"},{"pid":"ec480df3fc2021d56cf3ebaeb3103c62d0f7cf15","tid":446083,"uid":60219,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T04:02:15.000Z","msg":"補充返少少<br />\n<br />\n我覺得我係B公司見工既表現都唔錯，但唔敢講係咪超班"},{"pid":"5378d01b239bce60ed31bc576173cd8579a1cb55","tid":446083,"uid":75692,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T04:03:09.000Z","msg":"fg 30k-50k <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"055b3f849c9f8e40264d7fa48780c2dee37a7a96","tid":446083,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T04:03:33.000Z","msg":"差一個月都唔等得?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n50k返兩個月已經多過30k返三個月啦 咁都仲要問<br />\nbtw咩工咁高人工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04e7648832eeb970e39583ac51b06b4729aa22f1","tid":446083,"uid":57962,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T04:04:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0083e4e3c67209b4c53bfdbf58e3312a08db4e7c","tid":446083,"uid":60219,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T04:06:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>差一個月都唔等得?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n50k返兩個月已經多過30k返三個月啦 咁都仲要問<br />\nbtw咩工咁高人工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有另外一個問題既<br />\n<br />\n就係呢行大概30K既offer都會係12月前出晒<br />\n<br />\n如果我係12月未收到任何offer，係呢個工作市場剩低既機會可能只係約莫20k左右"},{"pid":"5bf85d8118b092176b348869823561854c4f299d","tid":446083,"uid":51904,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T04:09:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我今年final year，呢排忙緊見工<br />\n<br />\n前排A公司出30k既offer比我<br />\n<br />\n其實我等緊B公司份50k既offer，B公司既工作性質同埋成就感都比A公司高，但最衰就係B公司係絕無例外11月尾先出offer<br />\n<br />\n如果我而家接咗A公司既offer，日後我又接B公司既offer，呢行行規係我會需要承受賠償既風險，亦有可能被人告<br />\n<br />\n我無父幹無樓無車，到底我應該點選擇?<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 保守d揀A公司，起碼保證到日後買到樓<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 趁後生搏一舖啦屌你，搏盡無悔啊</blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.hk-lawyer.org/tc/content/%E6%8B%9B%E8%81%98%E5%AF%A6%E7%BF%92%E5%BE%8B%E5%B8%AB%E8%89%AF%E5%A5%BD%E5%AF%A6%E5%8B%99%E5%AE%88%E5%89%87\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk-lawyer.org%2Ftc%2Fcontent%2F%25E6%258B%259B%25E8%2581%2598%25E5%25AF%25A6%25E7%25BF%2592%25E5%25BE%258B%25E5%25B8%25AB%25E8%2589%25AF%25E5%25A5%25BD%25E5%25AF%25A6%25E5%258B%2599%25E5%25AE%2588%25E5%2589%2587&d=KHW6nftp2oq6oQc8USE1U54f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=284ad8aa\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.hk-lawyer.org/tc/content/%E6%8B%9B%E8%81%98%E5%AF%A6%E7%BF%92%E5%BE%8B%E5%B8%AB%E8%89%AF%E5%A5%BD%E5%AF%A6%E5%8B%99%E5%AE%88%E5%89%87</a><br />\n<br />\n儘管《守則》有所規定，律師會自2013年發表《守則》以來收到3間律師行關於申請人為了接受其他聘約而違反實習僱傭合約的通知。為確保實習律師在申請註冊實習律師合約時，律師會知悉此類行為，「實習律師合約註冊申請書」自2017年6月5日起已作出修訂，要求申請人聲明是否已遵守《守則》第9條。<br />\n<br />\n比人寫信去law soc port9你就hihi"},{"pid":"932fad09b517017f57fc6f3142436a878f5dbf93","tid":446083,"uid":60219,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T04:18:54.000Z","msg":"唉，心煩到溫唔到書做唔到功課<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n而家我女朋友搵緊14k，我同佢都唔大洗，我好希望一grad可以同佢一齊出去住<br />\n<br />\n如果我揀A公司，我同佢加埋過40k，買樓租樓生活開支都可以輕鬆解決，保守d揀A公司真係好吸引<br />\n<br />\n但我內心係最想做B公司，之前為咗佢個interview用咗幾個星期時間準備<br />\n<br />\n心郁郁想搏一舖但又怕兩頭唔到岸"},{"pid":"f84d8bcb73c29c2a2001ed0b7f2c1e13c2071879","tid":446083,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T04:24:31.000Z","msg":"40k你想買到樓?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其實真係睇你地點plan將來"},{"pid":"55a3f38a53d2c488a87209dd750020c19955e3e2","tid":446083,"uid":74171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T04:27:20.000Z","msg":"要賠幾多？"},{"pid":"b7722d96116ae6ea0a6a5d21b64c16627bfe55aa","tid":446083,"uid":60219,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T04:33:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>要賠幾多？</blockquote><br />\n唔會賠唔起既，賠錢係為咗令佢唔好告我/向呢行既紀律委員會port鳩我<br />\n<br />\n舊年個委員會好似已經嚴謹咗，聽聞今年會更重手<br />\n<br />\n好視乎間公司肯唔肯放你一馬"},{"pid":"88dd07b9c10c661d178423bd15b346b7bb66ef9c","tid":446083,"uid":69886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T04:36:09.000Z","msg":"無得同A講話去旅行先？"},{"pid":"4727ba5d4ae7c11e43f0adaf009f5f1431c378e2","tid":446083,"uid":60219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T04:39:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>無得同A講話去旅行先？</blockquote><br />\n拖唔到1個月<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8b4f42ba4ecbd5aa5e79a391b1c1afd57761ce8","tid":446083,"uid":51904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T04:40:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>要賠幾多？</blockquote><br />\n唔會賠唔起既，賠錢係為咗令佢唔好告我/向呢行既紀律委員會port鳩我<br />\n<br />\n舊年個委員會好似已經嚴謹咗，聽聞今年會更重手<br />\n<br />\n好視乎間公司肯唔肯放你一馬</blockquote><br />\n而家好似張Form AA要宣誓話你comply with code of good practice <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔係人地放唔放過你咁簡單"},{"pid":"29ba9dd5327a1d57d61131a8d080361c71f5bae0","tid":446083,"uid":74171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T04:57:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>無得同A講話去旅行先？</blockquote><br />\n拖唔到1個月<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n又唔係同佢打一世工，做住a先得唔得?"},{"pid":"c6d64b092285b4f67164ed6915949285c3a6344f","tid":446083,"uid":60219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T06:37:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>無得同A講話去旅行先？</blockquote><br />\n拖唔到1個月<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n又唔係同佢打一世工，做住a先得唔得?</blockquote><br />\n做咗a就預頭幾年都轉唔返去b<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a45859d810784f1c3d170d6cf3a15ca69cdd8413","tid":446083,"uid":60219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T07:05:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>要賠幾多？</blockquote><br />\n唔會賠唔起既，賠錢係為咗令佢唔好告我/向呢行既紀律委員會port鳩我<br />\n<br />\n舊年個委員會好似已經嚴謹咗，聽聞今年會更重手<br />\n<br />\n好視乎間公司肯唔肯放你一馬</blockquote><br />\n而家好似張Form AA要宣誓話你comply with code of good practice <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔係人地放唔放過你咁簡單</blockquote><br />\n驚到震<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b312774ea52fcddba9daa1593d244543dfcd1590","tid":446083,"uid":48321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T08:08:17.000Z","msg":"如果真係想等b公司，interview 果陣話自己會旅行,要12月先返到工，睇下佢咩反應啦"},{"pid":"1bbe35a2639417bfe07944ca7dfa4f5c293f9c33","tid":446083,"uid":60219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T08:26:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果真係想等b公司，interview 果陣話自己會旅行,要12月先返到工，睇下佢咩反應啦</blockquote><br />\nfinal year jj返緊學，搵既工都係下年暑假後先開始<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdae75b9fe817f742aa4f34d2643f1fd6c38172f","tid":446083,"uid":60219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T10:32:18.000Z","msg":"零正評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5026f5a2c934e8342ea05dc76ca5688be67f93e3","tid":446083,"uid":116622,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T10:41:55.000Z","msg":"當你最後無50k offer 得返20k嘅<br />\n一年後先搵得返份30k<br />\n你輸嘅係12萬 （30-20k)*12 你等唔等呢12萬開飯？<br />\n搏中咗唔止一年多24萬 仲有自豪感同滿足感<br />\n自己諗下"},{"pid":"0f902384aef23e4519960259f28e4d91769e2987","tid":446083,"uid":70205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T10:49:30.000Z","msg":"咩工fg 咁撚高人工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d500741c1d997b6f66eb5c075e61d070225a509a","tid":446083,"uid":38623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T10:53:16.000Z","msg":"我驚你咁串reject offer兩份工都無咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75614f8dee5dd19288c7038421cc9836f8ea1059","tid":446083,"uid":28668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T10:54:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咩工fg 咁撚高人工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nlaw"},{"pid":"9c02ca49dcb808f3d0e02d6afa3a7aeefeb3ec42","tid":446083,"uid":70205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T11:08:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>咩工fg 咁撚高人工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nlaw</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁撚高既咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}